00:02.553 --> 00:05.163
ï»¿Amazon founder and CEO Jeff Bezos...

00:05.250 --> 00:08.358
...has become the world's third richest person for the first time.

00:08.778 --> 00:11.992
According to Forbes magazine, Bezos passed Warren Buffett,...

00:12.239 --> 00:15.842
...the chairman and chief executive of Berkshire Hathaway Incorporated.

00:16.261 --> 00:22.651
Bezos' fortune was 65.3 billion dollars as of 4:30 p.m. Eastern time on Thursday,...

00:22.945 --> 00:26.177
...compared with Buffett's 64.9 billion dollars.

00:26.538 --> 00:31.442
Microsoft Corporation co-founder Bill Gates remained the world's richest person,...

00:31.666 --> 00:34.403
...at 77.7 billion dollars.

00:34.690 --> 00:40.089
Spain's Amancio Ortega, who founded the Zara clothing chain, and owner of Inditex,...

00:40.297 --> 00:43.715
...was second at 72.7 billion dollars.

00:44.031 --> 00:50.979
Facebook Incorporated co-founder and chief executive Mark Zuckerberg was fifth at 54 billion dollars.

